{"tid":223672,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"desktop 卡左起開機畫面跟著偵測唔到個mon","createTime":"2017-04-30T13:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T14:09:03.000Z","uid":8360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87a0e11dc6a1dc2af0b220574f4b7b4e444d3bf8","tid":223672,"uid":8360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:19:00.000Z","msg":"上個星期砌左部ryzen 1600 list<br />\n行雙mon,平時開機都無問題，但熄左機之後重開雖然會睇到開機畫面，但跟著個mon會入左休眠無反應，有無把打知咩事？<br />\n開機失敗之後，底板會長著左粒led:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vt60Cv8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvt60Cv8.jpg&h=4e3cccf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但只要熄左個總電源再重開就無事<br />\n平時開機成功就唔會著<br />\n依家每次開機都要熄個火牛電源或者插蘇再重新開機先入到window,有無大神知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c64d7e7a8c282114d2cd057fa210bd3a7247055","tid":223672,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:50:05.000Z","msg":"咩板"},{"pid":"997a8a6717286c9027417c4653c5db6a8593933b","tid":223672,"uid":8360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:09:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩板</blockquote><br />\nGA-AB350-Gaming-3"}]}